  audioProfileName: 
  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Welcome, recruit.


      I''ve heard stories of your bravery in
      the grove.


      It''s a pleasure to finally meet you in person.'
    nextOption: Thank you your highness
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: What can I help you with?
    nextOption: Here is a gift of cheese
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Oh lovely, you really are as impressive as they claimed.


      Thank
      you so much.  '
    nextOption: You Are Welcome
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Ser Invyncible said you had discovered something in the grove.


      Tell
      me about it.'
    nextOption: The dead came back to life
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'So it is true then?


      I thought the knight was just telling
      another drunken tale.'
    nextOption: I found these crystals on their bodies
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Oh no! [gasps]


      Normally anyone caught with those would
      be jailed instantly.


      Possession of mana has been banned since the War
      Of The Magi.'
    nextOption: Why?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Do you really not know?


      They did mention you were a bit
      odd, but I thought they were exagerating.


      Mana almost destroyed the
      world.'
    nextOption: So what are the chances you could help me find more?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Elemental mana like the kind you are holding hasn''t been seen
      for thousands of years.


      If it has re-emerged into the world it would
      be prudent to find out how and try to remedy the situation before another war
      breaks out.


'
    nextOption: So that's a yes?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Not so fast.


      I can''t send you out unprepared.


      What
      do you know about the purpose of the SunSworn.'
    nextOption: Nothing really
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'I figured as much.


      Go talk to Apprentice Historian Flare
      to learn about the history of the SunSworn.'
    nextOption: So I need a history lesson?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Indeed.


      The sunsworn exist to keep the world safe from
      magic.


      You must understand the threat we once conquered if you are
      to help us overcome it again.'
    nextOption: Ok, I'll talk to Flare now
  prerequisiteConditions:
